# package.json

# commands to Run inside  client folder:

npx create-react-app client

Then go into client folder:

cd client

Now install the extra packages used:

npm install axios react-router-dom simple-peer socket.io-client

# package-lock.json

# commands to run
Just run:

npm install

OR while installing packages:

npm install axios react-router-dom simple-peer socket.io-client

After running the command, npm automatically creates:

package-lock.json

client

├── node_modules

├── package.json

├── package-lock.json

└── src
